#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:2
msgid "Garbage Collected Types"
msgstr "垃圾回收类型"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:5
msgid "Registering GC Types"
msgstr "注册 GC 类型"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:8
msgid "GC Type Flag"
msgstr "GC 类型标志"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:10
msgid ""
"Add the flag ``asOBJ_GC`` to the binding generator to mark the type as "
"garbage collected."
msgstr ""
"将 ``asOBJ_GC`` 标志添加到绑定生成器，"
"以将类型标记为垃圾回收类型。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:22
msgid "GC Behaviours of Reference Types"
msgstr "引用类型的 GC 行为"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:24
msgid ""
"The process of determining the dead objects uses the first four of the "
"behaviours below, while the destruction of the objects is done by forcing"
" the release of the object's references."
msgstr ""
"确定死亡对象的过程使用下面的前四个行为，"
"而对象的销毁则通过强制释放对象的引用来完成。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:27
msgid "Example implementation of a garbage collected type:"
msgstr "垃圾回收类型的示例实现："

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:72
msgid "Registering the GC behaviours:"
msgstr "注册 GC 行为："

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:89
msgid ""
"You should remember to clear the GC flag in functions for increasing and "
"decreasing reference count. Otherwise it is possible that the GC "
"incorrectly determines that the object should be destroyed."
msgstr ""
"您应该记得在增加和减少引用计数的函数中清除 GC 标志。"
"否则 GC 可能会错误地判断该对象应被销毁。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:107
msgid ""
"`You can also read the official document about the GC behaviours "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_gc_object.html#doc_reg_gcref_1>`_."
msgstr ""
"`您也可以阅读关于 GC 行为的官方文档 "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_gc_object.html#doc_reg_gcref_1>`_。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:110
msgid "Garbage Collected Value Types"
msgstr "垃圾回收值类型"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:112
msgid ""
"Value types are normally not thought of as being part of circular "
"references as they themselves cannot be referenced. However, if a value "
"type can hold a reference to a type, and then that type can have the "
"value type as a member, a circular reference can be established "
"preventing the reference type from being released."
msgstr ""
"值类型通常不被认为是循环引用的一部分，"
"因为它们本身不能被引用。"
"然而，如果一个值类型可以持有对某个类型的引用，"
"而该类型又可以将该值类型作为成员，"
"那么就可能建立循环引用，从而阻止引用类型被释放。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:116
msgid ""
"You only need behaviours of ``asBEHAVE_ENUMREFS`` and "
"``asBEHAVE_RELEASEREFS`` for a value type."
msgstr ""
"对于值类型，您只需要 ``asBEHAVE_ENUMREFS`` 和 "
"``asBEHAVE_RELEASEREFS`` 行为。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:118
msgid ""
"Here is an example from the ``script_optional`` of asbind20 extension "
"library."
msgstr ""
"这是来自 asbind20 扩展库的 ``script_optional`` 的示例。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:127
msgid "Notifying GC of New Object"
msgstr "通知 GC 新对象"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:129
msgid ""
"The GC of AngelScript needs to know that a new object is created, this "
"can be done automatically by ``policies::notify_gc`` of asbind20."
msgstr ""
"AngelScript 的 GC 需要知道有新对象被创建，"
"这可以通过 asbind20 的 ``policies::notify_gc`` 自动完成。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:145
msgid ""
"If you need the ``asITypeInfo*`` in a factory function to notify GC, you "
"can use the (list) factory function with auxiliary object."
msgstr ""
"如果您需要在工厂函数中使用 ``asITypeInfo*`` 来通知 GC，"
"可以使用带有辅助对象的（列表）工厂函数。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/gc.rst:165
msgid ""
"If you create objects of garbage collected type from the application "
"side, you must also notify the garbage collector of its existence, so "
"it's a good idea to make sure all code uses the same way of creating "
"objects of this type."
msgstr ""
"如果从应用程序端创建垃圾回收类型的对象，"
"您还必须通知垃圾回收器其存在，"
"因此最好确保所有代码使用相同的方式创建此类型的对象。"

